tags.charge: Campground fees are $26.50 per day, and $150 per week (from April to October) and there is a two week limit. Off-season prices (from November to March) are $20 per day. Water is not available in the off season.
tags.description: Prairie Pines Campground features 95 lots, each with hookups for water, sewage and electric. The campground is open year round with handicap accessible restroom, shower, and laundry facilities.
tags.name: Prairie Pines Campground
